tweets.full_text:
This is Octant v2! üëÄüëÄ

"Octant v1 was an experiment to see if yield generated from a capital source could activate and support a community.

To a large degree, the answer has been yes. ‚úÖ

The Golem community back in 2021 was pretty idle at that time and has been totally reinvigorated with the engagement and utility the token now has to be able to participate in this Octant system.

Feeling comfortable with this system, Octant v2 is about scale and bringing this opportunity to other organizations." @vpabundance

James delves into how Octant v2 serves as the connective tissue between web3 treasuries, native web3 financial tools, and the incentives they create, linking them to base-layer Ethereum impactful projects that require sustainable funding.
